EmailTemplate.name: KOM Thank you for coming
EmailTemplate.subject: Kindergarten Open Morning: Thank you for coming!
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Dear {!Lead.FirstName}
Thank you so much for coming along to our Kindergarten Open Morning!It was wonderful to see you and {!Lead.Creche_no__c}, and to share our school community with you.
We hope you found the morning fun and insightful – and if you have any further questions, please don’t hesitate to contact me on 9286 9552 or via email.
For those of you that have applied for enrolment, we will be in touch to invite you in for an enrolment interview with our Head of Junior School Mrs Rhonda Robson. Kindergarten enrolment interviews are undertaken the year prior to commencing school.
If you are interested in enrolling your child at SACS, the next step is to complete and submit the attached Application for Enrolment form. If you would like to enrol your child in our 2016 intake, please contact us for an immediate enrolment interview, as positions are subject to availability.
In the meantime, keep updated with SACS:
You can find out what’s happening here at our St Andrew’s community by visiting our website, facebook page and our official youtube channel. They’re updated daily during term time with news, photos, events and mini videos.
I look forward to hearing from you soon. Thank you again for taking the time to visit St Andrew's and considering our school for the important education and development of your child.
Regards,
Bruce Perry
Registrar
St Andrew's Cathedral School
Sydney Square, Sydney NSW 2000, Australia
direct 9286 9552 mobile 0404 884 852 email bperry@sacs.nsw.edu.au phone +61 2 9286 9500 fax +61 29286 9550
